day and the next and a whole week, and they came to such a wilderness
that they could see neither earth nor sky, nor any living being, nor
any habitation; and in the deepest depth of this wilderness they met
another old man, even older than the first.        Hail, good
youths!        said he to the Tsareviches.        Are ye truants and
